        comment = "jsoncons C++ library maintainer"
    ))
Description: The jsoncons C++ library constructs representations from
    a JSON character vector. It includes extensions such as 'jsonpath'
    and 'jmespath' for flexible queries into JSON objects. This
    packages contains the complete header-only source for the library,
    plus simple R wrappers to support jsonpath and jmespath queries
    into JSON string representations.
License: BSL-1.0
LinkingTo: cpp11
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: C++11
